<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO SERIES - INSTALL - ROADRANGER VALVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>ROADRANGER VALVE</title>
        <para>To position the Roadranger valve, the range lever must be to the front or the splitter button to the left
            when facing forward.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Make sure the nut, valve cover, air lines, sheathing, and O-rings are in position on the
                lever shaft.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If previously removed, replace the air fittings (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p4">Figure 254</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017p4" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017p4" filename="../figg13/G13017p4.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 254. Roadranger Valve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the Roadranger valve on the lever shaft and rotate into position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p4">Figure 254</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">From the Roadranger valve bottom, tighten the jam nut (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p4">Figure 254</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the air lines to the air fittings (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p5">Figure 255</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017p5" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017p5" filename="../figg13/G13017p5.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 255. Tighten Jam Nut</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Slide the cover into position on the Roadranger valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p6">Figure 256</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017p6" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017p6" filename="../figg13/G13017p6.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 256. Valve Cover Mounting Screws</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the Roadranger valve cover two (2) mounting screws (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p6">Figure 256</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
